oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Cabinet card of Market Street area in Knoxville
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Cabinet card of Market Street area in Knoxville. The image features horses and carriages situated just outside storefronts on Market Street. The reverse of the card indicates that photographer, Drury Webb, is issuing the cabinet cards to introduce his new photo shop where "views of the village" and "frames to fit" are furnished for about cost.
